{"data":[{"date":"07:14 29/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Arsenal n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nguoi-arsenal-noi-do-cho-toi-do-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jens Lehmann cho bi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Mesut Ozil sa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng phanh v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1edbm k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng v\u00e0 nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 h\u01a1n. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi\u1ebfn Mannschaft \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ed5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 80 n\u0103m m\u1edbi kh\u1eafc ghi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil la mot trong nhung cau thu giau kinh nghiem thi dau quoc te nhat cua DT Duc tai World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/nguoi-arsenal-noi-do-cho-toi-do-tuyen-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 trong th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, t\u1eeb HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Manuel Neuer, Thomas Muller, Mats Hummels hay Jerome Boateng. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean r\u1ebd s\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho c\u1ea3 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mesut Ozil.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Xen gi\u1eefa chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn thua Mexico v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00e2u ch\u1ec9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, Ozil c\u00f2n d\u00ednh l\u00edu nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00ean l\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3, nh\u01b0 c\u00e3i nhau tay \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi C\u0110V hay c\u1ea3 chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh chung v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ozil th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Loew tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabu v\u1eady, anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 Arsenal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Jens Lehmann cho bi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng sa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng phanh th\u1eadm t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghe quen nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 n\u0103m tr\u1eddi qua r\u1ed3i. Anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi mong ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh trong v\u00f2ng 2-3 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Mesut l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 dai d\u1eb3ng. N\u1ebfu ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, ch\u1ee9 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng hay ho v\u1eeba qua c\u0169ng n\u00ean th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u cho Mesut. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng so v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-phai-chang-do-loi-nguyen-nha-vo-dich-465-189805.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng do l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-phai-chang-tuyen-duc-dang-tro-thanh-nhung-nguoi-anh-moi-421-189831.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1edbi?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-duc-bi-loai-tu-vong-bang-dau-roi-tinh-than-duc-466-189832.html\">Mannschaft b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i tinh th\u1ea7n \u0110\u1ee9c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-duc-ve-nuoc-som-boi-khong-co-hoa-hong-cho-nguoi-duc-tren-dat-nga-168-189858.html\">\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm: B\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa h\u1ed3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"701","checkdouble":"189918"},{"date":"07:43 29/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o trong ng\u00e0y Colombia ti\u1ec5n Senegal v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/nhung-hinh-anh-doc-dao-trong-ngay-colombia-tien-senegal-ve-nuoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c nhau \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Senegal t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nS\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Aliou Cisse ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a l\u00e0 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, khi ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Colombia &ndash; James Rodriguez g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 sau 30 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Senegal c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y ch\u00fat s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m n\u00e0o. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh g\u1eb7p v\u00f4 v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Trung v\u1ec7 Mina &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, \u0110T Colombia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong khi Senegal d\u00f9 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt, \u0111\u00e0nh cay \u0111\u1eafng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc do k\u00e9m h\u01a1n \u1edf ti\u00eau ch\u00ed Fair Play (nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n). Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a S\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, c\u1ea3 5 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh&nbsp;</strong><b>tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&nbsp;</b><strong>Colombia vs Senegal t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Senegal b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Senegal b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/073157-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1ed9t C\u0110V Senegal tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Senegal b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs Senegal b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/073202-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u1eabn l\u00e0 anh nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00eam chi\u1ebfc m\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\