3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nBatshuayi l\u1ea1i &ldquo;ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o&rdquo; Internet<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Michy Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Chelsea kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng&hellip; tr\u1eddi \u01a1i \u0111\u1ea5t h\u1ee1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o ph\u00fat 51 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Adnan Januzaj l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh, gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Batshuayi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ebfn \u00f4m l\u1ea5y qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 hay ho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng\" title=\"C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/bat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng thay v\u00ec s\u00fat v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u00f3ng&hellip; b\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i tr\u00fang m\u1eb7t anh. S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111ang t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t tr\u00ean Twitter, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ch\u00ednh &ldquo;kh\u1ed5 ch\u1ee7&rdquo; Batshuayi c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ahaha, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd &lsquo;\u0103n \u0111\u00f2n&rsquo; ch\u1ec9 1 ph\u00fat sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y m\u00e0. T\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady ch\u1ee9. \u0110au v\u00e3i&rdquo; &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 24 tu\u1ed5i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf tr\u00ean Twitter c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01b0\u1eddi ra n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng H.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem l\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/29/bat.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-189888.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/ket-qua-bi-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-189888.html\">Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (KT): C\u1ef1u sao tr\u1ebb M.U gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Tam s\u01b0</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"695","checkdouble":"189908"},{"date":"06:22 29/06","title":"Tr\u1eadn Colombia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/tran-colombia-se-la-cuoc-dau-knockout-lon-nhat-thap-ky-cua-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate sau tr\u1eadn thua Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai, Anh thua B\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj sau c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Man Utd. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Colombia kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/tran-colombia-se-la-cuoc-dau-knockout-lon-nhat-thap-ky-cua-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTr\u1eadn Colombia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 c\u1ee7a Anh.\u201d \u2013 Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Gareth Southgate trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bi-vs-anh-463-189888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9</span>. Th\u1eadt v\u1eady khi \u0111\u00e3 12 n\u0103m qua k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2006 \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, Tam S\u01b0 ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng th\u00eam n\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn knock-out n\u00e0o \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Euro.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u1edf Moscow sang tu\u1ea7n, HLV 47 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch x\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng cho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Southgate n\u00f3i th\u00eam: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng. B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay ch\u00ednh Colombia, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 Senegal n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y, ai c\u0169ng m\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t v\u00ec nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea3 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ai mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, Anh s\u1ebd r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m khi ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ho\u1eb7c Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/6-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-that-bai-trong-tinh-toan-cua-anh-truoc-bi-421-189905.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/tran-colombia-se-la-cuoc-dau-knockout-lon-nhat-thap-ky-cua-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/6-diem-sang-toi-nhin-tu-that-bai-trong-tinh-toan-cua-anh-truoc-bi-421-189905.html\">6 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t\u2026 m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Premier League \u2013 Adnan Januzaj, c\u1ef1u th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Man Utd. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Anh 0-1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"694","checkdouble":"189909"},{"date":"05:03 29/06","title":"Adnan Januzaj n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho \u0110T B\u1ec9?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/adnan-januzaj-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-dt-bi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh, HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTam S\u01b0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; Gareth Southgate m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 20/23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. \u0110\u00e1ng ra t\u00f4i n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee5c, v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec xa h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9\" title=\"Southgate \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/lam-tro-meo-de-duoc-thua-bi-southgate-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a Harry Kane v\u00e0o trong 10 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eb3ng may b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo. HLV Gareth Southgate ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Colombia c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi-421-189915.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi-421-189915.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 2, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh da ne duoc nhanh dau tu than ben trai\" title=\"Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/knock.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n (b\u00ean tr\u00e1i)</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Batshuayi ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o MXH v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi-421-189912.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi-421-189912.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong &ldquo;tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec&rdquo; gi\u1eefa Anh vs B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng G, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"693","checkdouble":"189910"},{"date":"04:38 29/06","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua sau tr\u1eadn Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-sau-tran-anh-01-bi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Anh vs B\u1ec9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1 - </strong>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho \u0110TQG sau 9 tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/adnan-januzaj-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-dt-bi.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Adnan Januzaj ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>25 tu\u1ed5i 251 ng\u00e0y -</strong> \u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 25 tu\u1ed5i 251 ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002 (25 tu\u1ed5i 207 ng\u00e0y).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>8 &ndash; </strong>Gi\u1eefa tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Panama v\u00e0 B\u1ec9, Anh c\u00f3 8 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf World Cup, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Uruguay v\u00e0 Costa Rica v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014 (9).</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>3 - </strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Anh vs B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 B\u1ec9, Croatia v\u00e0 Uruguay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>11 &ndash;</strong> Anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 11 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ghi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Panama.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Anh vs B\u1ec9 - B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Anh vs B\u1ec9 - B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Thong-ke-Anh-vs-Bi---Bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>4 - </strong>Trent Alexander-Arnold (19 tu\u1ed5i, 264 ng\u00e0y), l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ee9 4 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup, sau Luke Shaw, Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Michael Owen.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<strong>20 - </strong>S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Danny Welbeck t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 Anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 20/23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"692","checkdouble":"189911"},{"date":"05:00 29/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong \u201ctr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec\u201d gi\u1eefa Anh vs B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng G, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u1ea1ng sang<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup, c\u00e1c C\u0110V hi\u1ebfm khi n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady, gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Anh l\u1eabn B\u1ec9, khi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 sao &ldquo;ni\u1ec1m vui th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i&rdquo; c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn l\u1ea5y 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9, b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"C\u0110 B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u0110 B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1ecd nhu\u1ed9m \u0111\u1ecf c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i SV\u0110</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"C\u0110V Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 \u1ea3nh 4\" tit