111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Batshuayi ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o MXH v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"691","checkdouble":"189912"},{"date":"05:22 29/06","title":"L\u00e0m \"tr\u00f2 m\u00e8o\" \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thua B\u1ec9, Southgate n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/lam-tro-meo-de-duoc-thua-bi-southgate-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh, HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTam S\u01b0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; Gareth Southgate m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u. &ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 20/23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. \u0110\u00e1ng ra t\u00f4i n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u00f9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee5c, v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec xa h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9\" title=\"Southgate \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/lam-tro-meo-de-duoc-thua-bi-southgate-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a Harry Kane v\u00e0o trong 10 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eb3ng may b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo. HLV Gareth Southgate ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Colombia c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi-421-189915.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi-421-189915.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 2, qua \u0111\u00f3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh da ne duoc nhanh dau tu than ben trai\" title=\"Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/knock.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n (b\u00ean tr\u00e1i)</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Batshuayi ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o MXH v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi-421-189912.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-dang-nho-trong-tran-quyet-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-giua-anh-vs-bi-421-189912.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong &ldquo;tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec&rdquo; gi\u1eefa Anh vs B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng G, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs B\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"690","checkdouble":"189913"},{"date":"05:54 29/06","title":"HLV Martinez t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng sau khi \u201cl\u1ee1\u201d th\u1eafng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hlv-martinez-to-ra-hai-long-sau-khi-lo-thang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110T Anh.\r\n</h2><h2>Martinez h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 t\u1ea1i World Cup, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd mong ch\u1edd t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng khi b\u1ea1n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 World Cup, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110T Anh\" title=\"Roberto Martinez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/hlv-martinez-to-ra-hai-long-sau-khi-lo-thang-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, v\u00e0 Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Colombia. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 suy ngh\u0129 n\u00e0o xa h\u01a1n th\u1ebf, b\u1ea1n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng &ndash; \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1eb3ng ai ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Moscow v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec trong suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh da ne duoc nhanh dau tu than ben trai\" title=\"Anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n b\u00ean tr\u00e1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/knock.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ec9 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eed th\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-189908.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Batshuayi ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea3o MXH v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng ngu ng\u1ed1c nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Michy Batshuayi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bi-vs-anh-461-189901.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Anh 0-1 B\u1ec9 (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lam-tro-meo-de-duoc-thua-bi-southgate-noi-gi-421-189913.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/lam-tro-meo-de-duoc-thua-bi-southgate-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lam-tro-meo-de-duoc-thua-bi-southgate-noi-gi-421-189913.html\">L\u00e0m tr\u00f2 m\u00e8o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thua B\u1ec9, Southgate n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nSau khi v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh, HLV Gareth Southgate chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"689","checkdouble":"189914"},{"date":"05:57 29/06","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Adnan Januzaj</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G, HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Adnan Januzaj \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-2-1 anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Fellaini \u0111\u00e1 ngay sau trung phong Michy Batshuayi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs B\u1ec9 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs B\u1ec9 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Du-am-Anh-vs-Bi-bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Adnan Januzaj l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Januzaj l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T B\u1ec9, anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 51, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Youri Tielemans, c\u1ef1u sao M.U c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea3o ch\u00e2n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ebd n\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford d\u00f9 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1 v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi t\u1edbi b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i cho \u0110T B\u1ec9 sau 9 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/adnan-januzaj-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-dt-bi-421-189910.html\" target=\"_blank\">Adnan Januzaj n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9</span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Danny Rose</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Rose t\u1eebng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 d\u00e0i, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tay Ashley Young.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-Anh-vs-Bi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Rose g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Southgate, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng mang t\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 Rose c\u00f2n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u00e0n thua duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAdnan Januzaj \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Tam s\u01b0, Danny Rose d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u00e1p s\u00e1t. \u0110\u1ebfn khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i l\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i Rose, kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c g\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Jordan Pickford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Rose s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Young, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Tottenham b\u00e1n \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Trent Alexander-Arnold</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2, Trent Alexander-Arnold \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt h\u01a1n c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Danny\u00a0Rose r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trent Alexander-Arnold co mot tran dau an tuong\" title=\"Trent Alexander-Arnold c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/anot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trent Alexander-Arnold c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f3 78 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 2 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Anh (66 l\u1ea7n), ch\u1ec9 sau duy nh\u1ea5t Phil Jones. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Alexander-Arnold l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng, anh 1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u1ede kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 3 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3i nguy k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrent Alexander-Arnold \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, sau khi th\u0103ng hoa trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Michy Batshuayi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lukaku kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n, Batshuayi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u. Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Batshuayi\" title=\"Batshuayi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/hai-huoc-batshuayi-pha-dao-mxh-voi-man-an-mung-ngu-ngoc-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Batshuayi g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng theo ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 tung ra 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng cao, s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7m ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Batshuayi trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Batshuayi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, thay v\u00ec tung b\u00f3ng l\u00ean v\u00e0 s\u00fat th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00ec Batshuayi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang m\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh.\u00a0T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng chia s\u1ebb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Batshuayi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Lukaku cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate rut ra rat nhieu bai hoc sau tran Anh vs Bi\" title=\"HLV Southgate r\u00fat ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/hlv-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate r\u00fat ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Trent Alexander-Arnold l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Danny Rose v\u00e0 Jamie Vardy l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, c\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Marcus Rashford, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. Rashford \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng ra ngo\u00e0i \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Roberto Martinez</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 thay t\u1edbi 10 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t so v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roberto Martinez tiec nuoi khi buoc phai dung dau bang G\" title=\"Roberto Martinez ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/hlv-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roberto Martinez ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Martinez \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, song \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf\u201d, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Roberto Martinez ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u HLV Everton khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t HLV c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng G, B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Selecao, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 8 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil. So v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Selecao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCon \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111ang than th\u1edf n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"688","checkdouble":"189915"},{"date":"06:19 29/06","title":"T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Eric Dier l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/tat-ca-deu-hieu-chi-mot-minh-eric-dier-la-khong-hieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Eric Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn thua tr\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1. Ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eric Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Eric Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Eric-Dier-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Anh-vs-Bi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Adnan Januzaj khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n ma \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng, theo \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu Anh thay 8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama th\u00ec th\u1eadm ch\u00ed B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i duy nh\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois so v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u00e0n xem ai thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ghi b\u00e0n, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t ch\u0103m ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb. Trong hi\u1ec7p 1 B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn 2 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 5-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 tai n\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi B\u1ec9, Adnan Januzaj v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Roberto Martinez. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao M.U \u1edf ph\u00fat 51 khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-martinez-to-ra-hai-long-sau-khi-lo-thang-anh-421-189914.html\" target=\"_blank\"> HLV Roberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</span>, \u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Anh vs B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Trong khi&nbsp;\u0111\u00f3 Anh t\u1ecf ra vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Eric Dier kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eric Dier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn thua tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eric Dier noi ve tran Anh vs Bi\" title=\"Eric Dier n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/tat-ca-deu-hieu-chi-mot-minh-eric-dier-la-khong-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Eric Dier n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i phung ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, thua m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi-421-189915.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-dai-chien-vi-ngoi-nhi-bang-giua-anh-va-bi-421-189915.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs B\u1ec9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nEric Dier v\u1eabn \u0111ang th\u1eafc m\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i sao Anh l\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, ch\u1eafc c\u00f3 l\u1ebd anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ee5ng \u00fd s\u00e2u xa t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Gareth Southgate c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"687","checkdouble":"189916"}]}